OL,3,CGuernsey loses over half of its
OL,4,Chedgerows with fences partly to blame
OL,6,FCharlotte blames the lack of natural
OL,7,Fhabitats on new housing developments,
OL,8,Fwhere residents choose to remove or
OL,9,Freplace native hedgerows with non-
OL,10,Fnative species or fences that are
OL,11,Feasier to maintain.
OL,13,FCharlotte says it will be "interesting
OL,14,Fto see" if the downward trend for
OL,15,Fnative hedgerows continues until the
OL,16,Fnext State of Nature report comes out
OL,17,Fin five years.
