OL,3,CGuernsey loses over half of its
OL,4,Chedgerows with fences partly to blame
OL,6,FJack Etheridge, who grows native
OL,7,Fhedgerows including willow, hawthorn
OL,8,Fand elderflower to harvest fruit from,
OL,9,Falso says some islanders' decisions to
OL,10,Fintroduce non-native evergreen
OL,11,Fhedgerows on their properties is
OL,12,Fcausing problems.
OL,14,FHe explains: "Most people want their
OL,15,Fhedges to be evergreen and there's not
OL,16,Fan awful lot of native evergreens.
