OL,3,CGuernsey loses over half of its
OL,4,Chedgerows with fences partly to blame
OL,6,F"People want a fence, but it's all
OL,7,Fpersonal preference. Again, it's what
OL,8,Fthe people want.
OL,10,F"You can't go and stick a six-foot
OL,11,Fhedge up alongside a road. You'd have
OL,12,Fto get planning for it and obviously
OL,13,Fsome people do get planning, some
OL,14,Fdon't."
